 is no Muslim on earth who calls upon Allah in supplication but that Allah will grant it to him or divert some evil away from him, so long as he does not ask for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41864,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/03\/21\/refuge-harm-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":20051,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from harming another Muslim","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 21, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Rashid reported: I came to Abdullah ibn Amr, and I said, \u201cNarrate to me what you have heard from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Abdullah set out a scroll, and he said, \u201cThis is what the Messenger of Allah has written for me.\u201d I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19013,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/07\/seek-refuge-seven-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":20051,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Death: Seek refuge in Allah from seven deaths","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeek refuge in Allah from seven kinds of death: a sudden death, a snake bite, a predator, a fire, drowning, something falling above or below, and being killed whilst fleeing a marching army.\u201d Source: Musnad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u06